sys_update_xml.name: sp_css_edb17335dbe3e70054d8ff621f9619d6
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>.body {
 font-family: "SourceSansPro", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
}
b {
  font-weight:bold;
  font-size:1.5em;
}
a {
  cursor: pointer;
}
body {
  height:auto;
}
.touch_scroll{
  overflow:auto !important;
}
.label-hidden {
    display: none;
}
a:focus,
input:focus,
select:focus,
textarea:focus,
button:focus {
    outline: none;
}
.padding-top{
  padding-top: 0px !important;
}
table{
  font-size:13px;
}
/* header */
#survey-logo{
  position:relative;
  width:100%;
  float:left;
}
.logo{
	padding-left:0px;
}
.nci-logo {
    height: 92px;
}

#survey-nav{
  position:relative;
  width:100%;
  height:50px;
  background-color:#4A5F93;
  float:left;
}
#survey-nav .details {
  color:white;
  font-weight:bold;
  font-size:1.8rem;
  height:50px;
  line-height:50px;
}
.userInfo-block{
  float:right;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.userInfo-text:hover{
  cursor: pointer;
}
/* pagination */
.pagination {
    margin: 0px !important;
}
.tab-paging-section{
  text-align:center;
  padding-top:5px;
  height: 50px;
}
.tab-paging-setting{
  float:right;
  min-width:100px;
}
.tab-paging-label{
  text-align:right;
  float:right;
  padding:5px 10px;
}
/* Main*/
#survey-main{
  padding:0px;
}
.survey-block{
  min-width:1000px;
}
.top-menu{
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0px;
  display:flex;
}
.menu-item{
  width:200px;
  height: 35px;
  line-height: 35px;
  text-align: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
}
.menu-item.active{
  border-top: 1px solid gray;
  border-left: 1px solid gray;
  border-right: 1px solid gray;
  border-radius: 5px 5px 0px 0px;
  border-bottom: 0px;
}
.menu-item-last{
  border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
  width: calc(100% - 400px);
}
.main-content{
  border: 1px solid gray;
  border-top: 0px;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
  min-height: 600px; 
}
.message-box{
  margin-top: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding-left: 20px;
  padding-right: 20px;
}
.survey-form-section{
  padding-top:20px;
  border-top:1px dashed gray;
}
.basic-info{
  padding-bottom:10px;
}
.survey-button-section{
  text-align:center;
  padding-bottom:20px;
}
.survey-button-section button{
  padding-left: 40px;
  padding-right: 40px;
}
.mark-red{
  color:red;
}
/* form page */
.form-section{
  padding:5px 0px;
}
.form-section input[type="radio"]{
  margin-left:10px;
  cursor:pointer;
}
.indent-1{
  padding-left: 10px;
}
.indent-2{
  padding-left: 30px;
}
.indent-3{
  padding-left: 50px;
}
.indent-4{
  padding-left: 70px;
}
.indent-5{
  padding-left: 90px;
}

/* permission page */
.permission_content{
  padding: 100px 0px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 20px;
}
/* footer */
#footer{
  min-width:1020px;
}
#footer .footer-claim{
  text-align:center;
}
#footer .alert-info {
    color: #31708f;
    background-color: #d9edf7;
    border-color: #bce8f1;
    text-align: center;
}
#footer .alert {
    padding: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 4px;
}
#footer .footer-box{
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 0 0 0;
    padding: 30px 0 30px 0;
    border-top: 3px #4A5F93 solid;
}
.footer-box ul.footer-nav {
    display: block;
    width: auto;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 100%;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 0 0;
}
.footer-box .footer-nav li {
    color: #135B5D;
    text-align: center;
    display: inline;
    margin: 0 0 0 0;
    padding: 2px 0;
    background: url(bg_footer_nav.png) center right no-repeat;
}
.footer-box .footer-nav a {
    margin: 0 12px 0 6px;
    padding: 2px 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px #fff solid;
    transition: all 200ms ease-out;
}
.footer-box .footer-nav a:hover {
    color: #66665D;
    border-bottom: 1px #91908A solid;
}
.footer-box .footer-nav li.no-right {

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>GET</http_method><name>getAllSurvey</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	result = {};
	result.metadata = {};
	result.list = [];
	
	
	var dict = {};
	var rec = new GlideRecord('sys_documentation');
		rec.addQuery('name','x_naci_survey_partnership_program_survey');
		rec.query();
		while(rec.next()){
		  var item = {};
		  item.element = rec.getDisplayValue('element');
		  item.help = rec.getDisplayValue('help');
		  dict[item.element] = item.help;
		}

	result.metadata =  dict;
	
	var survey = new GlideRecord('x_naci_survey_partnership_program_survey');
		survey.query();
	while(survey.next()){
		var item = {};
		item.number = survey.number.toString();
		item.submit_for = survey.submit_for.name.toString();
		item.submit_by = survey.submit_by.name.toString();
		item.partnership = survey.partnership.toString();
		item.relationship = survey.relationship.toString();
		item.supply_document = survey.supply_document.toString();
		item.other_organization = survey.other_organization.toString();
		item.specifics = survey.specifics.toString();
		item.renewal = survey.renewal.toString();
		item.renewal_specify = survey.renewal_specify.toString();
		item.foa = survey.foa.toString();
		item.foa_specify = survey.foa_specify.toString();
		item.clearance = survey.clearance.toString();
		item.clearance_specify = survey.clearance_specify.toString();
		item.risk = survey.risk.toString();
		item.risk_document = survey.risk_document.toString();
		item.study_design = survey.study_design.toString();
		item.design_document = survey.design_document.toString();
		item.intellectual = survey.intellectual.toString();
		item.contribution = survey.contribution.toString();
		item.interventional = survey.interventional.toString();
		item.risk_assessed = survey.risk_assessed.toString();
		item.entity = survey.entity.toString();
		item.monetary = survey.monetary.toString();
		item.amount = survey.amount.toString();
		item.amount_type = survey.amount_type.toString();
		item.no_assets = survey.no_assets.toString();
		item.industry_scrutiny = survey.industry_scrutiny.toString();
		item.industry_use = survey.industry_use.toString();
		item.industry_use_specify = survey.industry_use_specify.toString();
		item.nonprofit_scrutiny = survey.nonprofit_scrutiny.toString();
		item.nonprofit_aim = survey.nonprofit_aim.toString();
		item.nonprofit_aim_specify = survey.nonprofit_aim_specify.toString();
		item.participate = survey.participate.toString();
		item.solicitation = survey.solicitation.toString();
		item.advisory = survey.advisory.toString();
		item.advisory_specify = survey.advisory_specify.toString();
		item.confidential_detail = survey.confidential_detail.toString();
		item.confidential_specify = survey.confidential_specify.toString();
		item.complaints = survey.complaints.toString();
		item.complaints_specify = survey.complaints_specify.toString();
		item.involved = survey.involved.toString();
		item.disclosure = survey.disclosure.toString();
		item.management = survey.management.toString();
		item.communicate = survey.communicate.toString();
		item.communicate_specify = survey.communicate_specify.toString();
		item.inequitable_treatment = survey.inequitable_treatment.toString();
		item.inequitable_treatment_specify = survey.inequitable_treatment_specify.toString();
		item.doc = survey.doc.toString();
		result.list.push(item);
	}
	
	return result;

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_survey/partnership_program_survey/getAllSurvey</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/getAllSurvey</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-11 23:15:07</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>22ed7ff5db2f6b00b86770c08c961993</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>getAllSurvey</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Partnership program process survey" source="x_naci_survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Partnership program process survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_22ed7ff5db2f6b00b86770c08c961993</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>yuw5@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-02-13 02:05:32</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Partnership Program Survey">a69db379db2f6b00b86770c08c9619b2</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>tags-input{display:block}
tags-input *,tags-input :after,tags-input :before{-moz-box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-box-sizing:border-box;box-sizing:border-box}
tags-input .host{position:relative;
  /*
  margin-top:5px;
  margin-bottom:5px;
  */
  height:100%}
tags-input .host:active{outline:0}
tags-input .tags{-moz-appearance:textfield;-webkit-appearance:textfield;padding:1px;overflow:hidden;word-wrap:break-word;cursor:text;background-color:#fff;
  /*
  border:1px solid #a9a9a9;
  box-shadow:1px 1px 1px 0 #d3d3d3 inset;
  */
  height:100%}
tags-input .tags.focused{outline:0;-webkit-box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(5,139,242,.6);-moz-box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(5,139,242,.6);
  box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(5,139,242,.6)}
tags-input .tags .tag-list{margin:0;padding:0;list-style-type:none}
tags-input .tags .tag-item{margin:2px;padding:0 5px;display:inline-block;float:left;font:14px "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
  height:26px;line-height:25px;border:1px solid #acacac;border-radius:3px;
  /*
  background:-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#f0f9ff 0,#cbebff 47%,#a1dbff 100%);
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#f0f9ff 0,#cbebff 47%,#a1dbff 100%)
  */
}
tags-input .tags .tag-item.selected{background:-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#febbbb 0,#fe9090 45%,#ff5c5c 100%);
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#febbbb 0,#fe9090 45%,#ff5c5c 100%)}
tags-input .tags .tag-item .remove-button{margin:0 0 0 5px;padding:0;border:none;background:0 0;
  cursor:pointer;vertical-align:middle;font:700 16px Arial,sans-serif;color:#585858}
tags-input .tags .input.invalid-tag,tags-input .tags .tag-item .remove-button:active{color:red}
tags-input .tags .input{border:0;outline:0;margin:2px;padding:0 0 0 5px;float:left;height:26px;font:14px "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif}
tags-input .tags .input::-ms-clear{display:none}
tags-input.ng-invalid .tags{-webkit-box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(255,0,0,.6);
  -moz-box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(255,0,0,.6);box-shadow:0 0 3px 1px rgba(255,0,0,.6)}
tags-input[disabled] .host:focus{outline:0}tags-input[disabled] .tags{background-color:#eee;cursor:default}
tags-input[disabled] .tags .tag-item{opacity:.65;background:-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#f0f9ff 0,rgba(203,235,255,.75) 47%,rgba(161,219,255,.62) 100%);
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#f0f9ff 0,rgba(203,235,255,.75) 47%,rgba(161,219,255,.62) 100%)}
tags-input[disabled] .tags .tag-item .remove-button{cursor:default}
tags-input[disabled] .tags .tag-item .remove-button:active{color:#585858}tags-input[disabled] .tags .input{background-color:#eee;cursor:default}
tags-input .autocomplete{margin-top:5px;position:fixed;padding:5px 0;z-index:999;width:calc(100% - 35px);background-color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  -webkit-box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.2);-moz-box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.2);box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}
tags-input .autocomplete .suggestion-list{margin:0;padding:0;list-style-type:none;max-height:280px;overflow-y:auto;position:relative}
tags-input .autocomplete .suggestion-item{padding:5px 10px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;
  font:14px "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#000;background-color:#fff}
tags-input .autocomplete .suggestion-item.selected,tags-input .autocomplete .suggestion-item.selected em{color:#fff;background-color:#0097cf}
tags-input .autocomplete .suggestion-item em{font:normal 700 14px "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#000;background-color:#fff}</css><name>partnership survey tag css</name><sys_class_name>sp_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-12 01:09:07</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b9f7d8cadb6f6b00b86770c08c961928</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>partnership survey tag css</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Partnership program process survey" source="x_naci_survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Partnership program process survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_css_b9f7d8cadb6f6b00b86770c08c961928</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-02-12 01:11:06</sys_updated_on></sp_css></record_update>

		survey.amount_type = param.amount_type.toString();
		survey.no_assets = param.no_assets.toString();
		survey.industry_scrutiny = param.industry_scrutiny.toString();
		survey.industry_use = param.industry_use.toString();
		survey.industry_use_specify = param.industry_use_specify.toString();
		survey.nonprofit_scrutiny = param.nonprofit_scrutiny.toString();
		survey.nonprofit_aim = param.nonprofit_aim.toString();
		survey.nonprofit_aim_specify = param.nonprofit_aim_specify.toString();
		survey.participate = param.participate.toString();
		survey.solicitation = param.solicitation.toString();
		survey.advisory = param.advisory.toString();

		survey.doc = param.doc.toString();
		var task_id = survey.insert();
	
		return {id: task_id};
	
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_survey/partnership_program_survey/submitSurvey</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/submitSurvey</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-11 23:14:29</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>11cd3779db2f6b00b86770c08c96199c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>submitSurvey</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Partnership program process survey" source="x_naci_survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Partnership program process survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_11cd3779db2f6b00b86770c08c96199c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>yuw5@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-02-13 01:46:43</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Partnership Program Survey">a69db379db2f6b00b86770c08c9619b2</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_c8b9b4d6dbabab00b86770c08c96192d
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>GET</http_method><name>getMissingSurvey</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {

	var ids = [];
	var staff = new GlideRecord('x_naci_survey_partnership_program_survey');
		staff.query();
		while(staff.next()){
			ids.push(staff.submit_for.sys_id);
		}

	var hasNotSubmit = [];
	var record = new GlideRecord('x_naci_survey_staff_for_survey');
		record.addQuery('user_id', 'NOT IN', ids.toString());
		record.query();
  
	while(record.next()){
       var item = {};
	   item.name = record.name.toString();
	   item.id = record.user_id.toString();
	   item.ic = record.ic.toString();	
	   hasNotSubmit.push(item);
	}

    return hasNotSubmit;

			}).then(resolve, reject);
		});
	};
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sp_angular_provider</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>yuw5@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-11 22:46:54</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>92367739dbe3e70054d8ff621f96194a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SurveyForm</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Partnership program process survey" source="x_naci_survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Partnership program process survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_angular_provider_92367739dbe3e70054d8ff621f96194a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>yuw5@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-02-12 00:50:56</sys_updated_on><type>service</type></sp_angular_provider></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_384a0482db6f6b00b86770c08c9619b4
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>GET</http_method><name>fetchUser</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var users = [];
	var firstName = request.queryParams.first.toString();
	var lastName = request.queryParams.last.toString();

	var user_item = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
	     
	if(firstName !== lastName) {
		var p = user_item.addQuery('first_name', 'STARTSWITH', firstName);
		p.addOrCondition('u_preferred_firstname','STARTSWITH', firstName);
		user_item.addQuery('last_name', 'STARTSWITH', lastName);
	}
	else{
		var tmp = user_item.addQuery('first_name', 'STARTSWITH', firstName);
		tmp.addOrCondition('u_preferred_firstname','STARTSWITH', firstName);
		tmp.addOrCondition('last_name', 'STARTSWITH', lastName)
	}
	user_item.query();
	 //var index = 0;
     while(user_item.next()){
		 var value = user_item.getDisplayValue('first_name') + " " + user_item.getDisplayValue('last_name');
		 var label = value;
		 var id = user_item.getDisplayValue('sys_id');
		 var email = user_item.getDisplayValue('email');
		 var phone = user_item.getDisplayValue('phone');
		 var title = user_item.getDisplayValue('title');
		 var org = user_item.getDisplayValue('u_long_org_division');
		 if (email) {
			 label += "  [" + email + "]";
		 }
		 users.push({label: label, value: value, id: id, email: email, phone: phone, title: title, org: org});
     }
   
     return users;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_survey/partnership_program_survey/fetchUser</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/fetchUser</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-02-12 00:08:54</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>384a0482db6f6b00b86770c08c9619b4</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>fetchUser</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Partnership program process survey" source="x_naci_survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Partnership program process survey">c3cce779dbeb6b00b86770c08c96191e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_384a0482db6f6b00b86770c08c9619b4</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>yuw5@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-02-12 22:31:02</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="Partnership Program Survey">a69db379db2f6b00b86770c08c9619b2</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>
